data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. MOTIVATED SELLER! SELLER IS GIVING BUYERS MONEY TOWARDS CLOSING COST! Rare find! Beautifully updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage w/den/flex room, fenced, pool home with no backyard neighbors. Low HOA and no CDD. Features include new flooring throughout, new roof, new hot water heater, vaulted ceilings, and recreational space in the garage complete with a lifestyle screen that includes a lifetime warranty. The kitchen, updated 3 years ago, boasts stainless steel appliances, granite counters and espresso cabinets with a pass through to the dining room, closet pantry and an area for a breakfast table overlooking the pool. The master suite offers a large walk in closet, direct access to the back patio and updated ensuite bathroom. Enjoy the Florida lifestyle from the pool outside with privacy fence, backing onto a green space. Conveniently located near I-4 and I-75 it's an easy commute to downtown Tampa, USF, MacDill, Tampa airport, 3 major league sports teams, Lakeland, 45 minutes to Disney and near major retail. A pool home at this location in this price point won't last long. Check out the 3D virtual tour link, then call for your private tour today!
